    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait why would i take vitamin K on the days i'm not taking the warfarin? i thought that's what makes the blood clot more... wouldn't that just cancel out the medicine i'm trying to take? also are you sure 2mg is enough to keep me safe? i just dont want to deal with the doctors every week for blood tests if i dont have to.",
